name: Arnel Cayabyab
text: For your amusement, here are some of the lyrics I remember. Medyo rated PG nga lang. Lol.    Listen to the rhythm of the silent night  Baby can't you hear what it's asking for  It is time again for me to score  It's time again for me to do it on the floor  But baby, if you cant do it tonight  I guess I'll have to do it solo flight    Then the earlier lines I gave are part of the chorus. Lol.    Previous bar owner where I used to play was also a member of snake pit.  :D
